  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uganda UNPRPD: Promoting the rights of persons with disabilities</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will focus on policy interventions by ensuring that the policy environment in Uganda becomes more conducive for the use of Inclusive Education and Access to Information. This will mainly be achieved through setting up a national Policy Board and Management Committee, the creation and adoption of a necessary policy for the use of Assistive Technology to ensure Inclusive Education and Access to Information for persons with visual and hearing impairments in Uganda. In addition, procurement and production guidelines will be created.</narrative>
  </description>
